title: Strange News: Immortal Worms Invade Virginia, Cruise Lines Begin to Reopen
itunes:title: Strange News: Immortal Worms Invade Virginia, Cruise Lines Begin to Reopen
description:
Some cruise lines begin to reopen. In Virginia, locals were astonished to find a bizarre, potentially immortal creature invading -- the infamous (and alien-like) Hammerhead Worm. Tune in for more in this week's Strange News segment.
